  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9e5fa7bf1d6fb8147abfaf1230a482d3, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "Also, I know you\u2019ve had issues falling asleep recently - Did you
    get that checked out? Narcolepsy is a serious condition, you know - And our insurance
    doesn\u2019t cover it. If it\u2019s really that bad, you should just try distracting
    yourself to stay awake - Like, play one of those \u2018video games\u2019 or touch
    a bobblehead, or something! It can\u2019t be that hard, especially when you know
    that you\u2019re making a difference in the world! Remember - Opportunities don't
    happen, you create them."
